      "description": "Hey there! I am absolutely thrilled to be listing this beauty. It has been my total pride and joy, and I've pampered it so much it honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It's in truly spectacular, flawless shape\u2014not a single mark on it and it drives like a dream. I'm so sad to see it go, but I'm looking for a great new home for it where it'll be just as loved. You really have to see it in person to believe how perfect it is. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
