    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of high-revving atmospheric engineering. At its heart is the S54B32 inline-six, featuring a 12.5:1 compression ratio and individual throttle bodies, delivering a crisp 8,000 RPM redline. This specimen has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance: the high-pressure VANOS system has been overhauled, rod bearings replaced with VAC treated shells, and the rear subframe reinforced with structural plates. Power is managed via a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox and an M Variable Differential Lock. The chassis retains its factory-fresh rigidity, complemented by original Style 67 forged wheels and a pristine interior free of bolster wear or pixel degradation. A definitive turn-key investment for the purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
