    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Presenting an absolute masterpiece of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in impeccable, showroom-ready condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment since day one. The exterior finish is flawless, retaining its deep, factory luster without a single swirl mark, chip, or blemish, thanks to regular professional detailing and a high-grade ceramic coating. Step inside to an interior that still carries the faint scent of new leather; the upholstery is taut and pristine, with no signs of wear on the bolsters or carpets. Every feature, from the advanced infotainment system to the dual-zone climate control, operates with precision. Under the hood, the engine bay is clean enough to display, housing a powertrain that has been serviced exclusively by authorized technicians using genuine parts. This is not just a used car; it is a time capsule that offers the exact driving experience and aesthetic appeal of a brand-new vehicle. Complete with all original keys, manuals, and a comprehensive service portfolio.",
      "price": 48500.0,
